@startuml
!theme plain
title 18. UA-Link Pod Domain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "xPU/GPU endpoints" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "UA-Link switches" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Pod scale-up domain" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Scheduler locality" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Coherence-CE" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : load/store/atomics
N2 --> N3 : switch fabric
N3 --> N4 : pod membership
N4 --> N5 : placement affinity

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
